      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_01_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_01_01-suz003.m4a",
      "text": "こればかりは解決の糸口が見えませんわ……",
      "startTime": 16.433333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_01_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_01_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "自画自賛しながら何を悩んでるんだ？",
      "startTime": 20.733333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_01_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_01_01-suz004.m4a",
      "text": "あら、{user}さん\n聞いていたんですの？",
      "startTime": 25.166666666666668,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_01_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_01_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "聞いてたんじゃなくて、勝手に聞こえてきたんだ",
      "startTime": 26.866666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
